    <h1>Helpful Content System</h1>
    <p class="description">Google's AI-powered, site-wide ranking signal that evaluates whether content is made primarily to help people or to manipulate search rankings — and rewards or demotes entire domains accordingly.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
